1- Integration with Online Services
    a- Pull book data from sources like Goodreads or Google Books
    b- Recomendations based on reading habits
2- Social features
    a- Share book reviews and ratings
    b- Book club discussion groups
3- Offline access
    a- Allow user to access the library and reading progress without an internet connection
4- Gamification
    a- Achievements or badges for milestones (e.g. completing a book or reading streaks)
5- Dark mode
    a- Provide dark theme for night-time use